   NOAA Satellite Service Division

                               PRIVACY NOTICE

   This computer system, including all related equipment, networks and
   network devices (specifically including internet access), are provided
   for general public and organizational use. NOAA computer systems may be
   monitored for all lawful purposes, including to ensure that their use
   is authorized to facilitate protection against unauthorized access, and
   to verify security procedures and operational security.

   During monitoring, information may be examined, recorded, copied and
   used for authorized purposes. Monitoring may result in open display of
   results. All information, including personal information, placed on or
   sent over this system may be monitored. Use of this NOAA/NESDIS
   computer system, authorized or unauthorized, constitutes consent to
   monitoring for these purposes.
